      <title>爱沙尼亚间谍头子称俄罗斯加大对波罗的海国家的威胁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/russia-ratchets-up-threat-to-baltics-estonia-spy-chief-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[爱沙尼亚反情报负责人表示，过去一年，俄罗斯间谍机构在波罗的海地区采取了更具侵略性的策略，包括炸弹恐慌、网络攻击和选举干扰。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/russia-ratchets-up-threat-to-baltics-estonia-spy-chief-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 16:29:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着选举临近，美国对更多中国芯片限制面临阻力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/us-faces-pushback-on-more-china-chip-curbs-as-election-nears</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国试图向荷兰和日本施压，要求其进一步限制中国获取半导体技术，但本周遭遇挫折，两国都在寻求时间让现有限制生效——看看谁在美国总统选举中获胜。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/us-faces-pushback-on-more-china-chip-curbs-as-election-nears</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 16:16:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>智利将难民遇害事件归咎于委内瑞拉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/chile-points-finger-at-venezuela-in-case-of-murdered-refugee</link>
      <description><![CDATA[智利政府要求委内瑞拉合作调查一名被谋杀的难民，有迹象表明这起谋杀案是出于政治动机，这考验了两国之间的关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/chile-points-finger-at-venezuela-in-case-of-murdered-refugee</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 16:14:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>岸田访问摇摆州丰田工厂，宣传日本在美国的投资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/kishida-touts-investments-with-visit-to-swing-state-toyota-plant</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本首相岸田文雄访问了丰田汽车公司位于北卡罗来纳州的一家工厂，试图强调日本在美国的投资。北卡罗来纳州是乔·拜登总统和唐纳德·特朗普总统 2024 年竞选的关键战场州。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/kishida-touts-investments-with-visit-to-swing-state-toyota-plant</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 16:04:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国气候大臣在大选前辞职</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/uk-climate-minister-stands-down-ahead-of-general-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[能源部长格雷厄姆·斯图尔特退出了英国首相里希·苏纳克的政府，因为他准备在未来几个月面临一场激烈的选举。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/uk-climate-minister-stands-down-ahead-of-general-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 16:01:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>壳牌气候呼吁促使荷兰集团推动更严格的规则</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/shell-climate-appeal-sees-dutch-group-push-for-tougher-rules</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一家荷兰环保组织正在推动对 2021 年壳牌公司削减碳排放量的具有里程碑意义的法院命令进行更严格的解释，试图将该公司对该判决的上诉转化为对自己有利的方式。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/shell-climate-appeal-sees-dutch-group-push-for-tougher-rules</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 15:38:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登还使用政治捐款来支付律师费用</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/like-trump-biden-used-political-donations-to-cover-lawyer-fees</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登曾批评共和党竞争对手唐纳德·特朗普依靠政治捐款来支付法律费用，他用民主党全国委员会筹集的近200万美元来支付自己的律师费。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/like-trump-biden-used-political-donations-to-cover-lawyer-fees</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 15:27:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>开发商将在加拿大住宅建设中获得廉价土地租赁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/developers-to-get-cheap-land-leases-in-canadian-homebuilding-push</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总理贾斯汀·特鲁多政府将向开发商提供公共土地的低成本租赁，并推动工厂化住宅建设，作为缓解加拿大住房危机的“历史性”计划的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/developers-to-get-cheap-land-leases-in-canadian-homebuilding-push</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 15:22:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴西与中国关系加深，卢拉与亿万富翁 JBS 兄弟重聚</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/lula-reunites-with-billionaire-jbs-brothers-as-brazil-s-china-ties-deepen</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亿万富翁巴蒂斯塔兄弟在被任命为 JBS SA 董事会成员后不到三周，就惊人地卷土重来，将他们推入巴西最高权力圈。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/lula-reunites-with-billionaire-jbs-brothers-as-brazil-s-china-ties-deepen</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 14:54:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>反 LGBTQ 法案成为加纳投票的政治烫手山芋</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/anti-lgbt-bill-becomes-political-hot-potato-for-ghana-elections</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加纳的两位总统候选人都谴责了同性恋，但没有表示他们是否会签署一项严厉的反 LGBTQ 法案，将其纳入可能对该国财政产生严重影响的法律。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/anti-lgbt-bill-becomes-political-hot-potato-for-ghana-elections</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 11:50:55 GMT</pubDate>
